## Dependencies

the controller is based on https://github.com/slater1/AdaptiveCruiseControl.git


## How to build

- Checkout the repo (and submodules)
```bash
$ git clone --recursive https://github.com/ytlei/midterm-project.git
cd path
mkdir -p build
cd build
cmake ..
make
```

